Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:32.60,DCMain,HIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:34.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Higo and Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:37.19,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Does "passionate couple" \Nrefer to Higo and Okino Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:40.07,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
